  "2398140": {
    "name": "Bail Force: Cyberpunk Bounty Hunters",
    "steam_appid": 2398140,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2398140/extras/462357123d012dff31b695aa9e9d4428.avif?t=1768581191\" width=780 height=80 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Welcome to New Rise City</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Step into the neon-soaked chaos of Bail Force: Cyberpunk Bounty Hunters, a high-octane action roguelite where every bounty leads you deeper into danger, and every enemy evolves with your playstyle.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2398140/extras/6d4d8b9957b326bba57f92b09fbe7afc.poster.avif?t=1768581191\" width=780 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2398140/extras/6d4d8b9957b326bba57f92b09fbe7afc.webm?t=1768581191\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2398140/extras/6d4d8b9957b326bba57f92b09fbe7afc.mp4?t=1768581191\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Merging the frenetic energy of classic arcade action with the dystopian edge of a cyberpunk underworld, Bail Force puts you in the boots of elite bounty hunters Angel or Lea, two bounty hunters with radically different motivations.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hunt down New Rise City's most dangerous criminals in tight 2D combat, using a deadly mix of melee and ranged weapons. Enhance your build mid-run with modular Add-Ons, and brace yourself for encounters that never play the same twice.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2398140/extras/20ed210e3d8cbd66fd6e9bae4c3caa92.avif?t=1768581191\" width=780 height=80 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Adaptive Combat System – Enemies That Learn</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Daring to push action roguelite design further, Bail Force introduces the Adaptive Combat System, a feature where enemies analyze your preferred fighting style and evolve to counter it.  Favor ranged weapons? Enemies will close the distance. Rely on dodging and dashing? They'll pin you down. These aren’t just stat bumps; this is enemy behavior shaped by <i>you</i>. The deeper into the city you go, the smarter and deadlier they become.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2398140/extras/d1ad42697da93c14791a22c4db92b9e2.poster.avif?t=1768581191\" width=780 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2398140/extras/d1ad42697da93c14791a22c4db92b9e2.webm?t=1768581191\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2398140/extras/d1ad42697da93c14791a22c4db92b9e2.mp4?t=1768581191\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Add-On Upgrade System</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect and equip Add-Ons to tailor your build with passive buffs and active ability enhancements. Create synergies with your preferred weapons or change tactics entirely as challenges evolve mid-run.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Two Hunters. One City. Colliding Destinies.</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose between <strong>Angel</strong>, a determined student out for revenge, or <strong>Lea</strong>, a sharp-edged survivor chasing her next big payday. While their motivations differ, their missions collide, and their fates are more connected than they realize.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2398140/extras/22932daef174b475e71054a42fd57cc9.poster.avif?t=1768581191\" width=780 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2398140/extras/22932daef174b475e71054a42fd57cc9.webm?t=1768581191\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2398140/extras/22932daef174b475e71054a42fd57cc9.mp4?t=1768581191\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You’ll face not only cybernetic enforcers and elite criminals, but also the shifting relationship between two bounty hunters caught in something bigger than themselves. Conflict, betrayal, and trust lie at the heart of a branching narrative that reacts to your choices.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your character selection and combat style shape the outcome. Whether you favor melee or ranged combat, how you fight affects what story you’ll unlock. With multiple endings and emotionally driven storylines, Bail Force delivers replayability rooted in both mechanics and meaning.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Narrative-Driven Replayability</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every decision matters. Each run offers a new perspective, and your evolving playstyle, combined with protagonist choice, leads to unique outcomes. Whether you're seeking closure or vengeance, Bail Force rewards experimentation with rich narrative discovery.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2398140/extras/77ec658ff4baa90943a6de1fc557d6e8.poster.avif?t=1768581191\" width=780 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2398140/extras/77ec658ff4baa90943a6de1fc557d6e8.webm?t=1768581191\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2398140/extras/77ec658ff4baa90943a6de1fc557d6e8.mp4?t=1768581191\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Classic Arcade Action Meets Modern Roguelite Progression</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Feel the rush of <strong>tight 2D action</strong> inspired by classic arcade combat. Run-and-gun, dash, slash, and combo your way through fast, responsive encounters, then unlock permanent upgrades between runs in classic roguelite fashion.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2398140/extras/2a17e4317009053a45068f507db80eaa.poster.avif?t=1768581191\" width=780 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2398140/extras/2a17e4317009053a45068f507db80eaa.webm?t=1768581191\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2398140/extras/2a17e4317009053a45068f507db80eaa.mp4?t=1768581191\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Procedural City Hunts</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >No two missions are the same. Explore procedurally generated city zones, adapt to randomized enemy loadouts and layouts, and chase criminals across dynamic cyberpunk environments.</p>",
